{"type":"message","id":"051e3272","parentId":"c0cce44f","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:00:04.844Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ad0c9469b013407d8725d5fa","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 以下描述的文件都在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt；\n- 如果存在可用脚本，优先复用，不满足当前场景时才允许创建新脚本。\n- 执行时严格按照要求的文件名称及后缀，防止执行到不存在的文件。\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、使用tushare-data skill，获取数据判断今日是否收盘，未收盘，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务；\n2、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n3、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n4、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 3.1、满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 3.2、只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n5、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n6、使用openclaw message send --channel feishu --account stock --target <user_id> --message <xxx> 命令，将数据通过飞书(feishu)渠道推送给用户ID为：ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5的用户；\n7、推送的数据格式参考alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773108004843}}
{"type":"message","id":"d29a277f","parentId":"051e3272","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:00:10.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the task. Let me break down what I need to do:\n\n1. Use tushare-data skill to check if the market is closed today. If closed, end the task. If not closed, continue.\n2. If realtime-data.txt has content, clear it. Otherwise, continue.\n3. Use tushare-data skill to get real-time stock data according to get-data-template.md format, save to realtime-data.txt.\n4. Filter the data according to alert-rules.md rules.\n5. If there's matching data, continue. Otherwise, end.\n6. Send the data via Feishu to user ID: ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5\n7. Use the format from alert-template.md\n\nLet me first check if there's a tushare-data skill and read the related template files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_823d6ca70d6e43a3b2c776f2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f2f6b1c49d364a7db209d0dc","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_944f3e4778b646b38ab7f835","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_388eb60ee9d948fcba35a068","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773108004844}}
{"type":"message","id":"8941b516","parentId":"d29a277f","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:00:10.390Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_823d6ca70d6e43a3b2c776f2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 (Stock Code) - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 (Stock Name) - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 (Current Price) - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 (Change %) - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额(Price Change) - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 (Timestamp) - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 昨收价 (Previous Close)\n- 今开价 (Open Price)\n- 最高价 (High)\n- 最低价 (Low)\n- 成交量 (Volume)\n- 成交额 (Amount)\n- 市盈率 (PE Ratio)\n- 总市值 (Market Cap)\n- 涨跌额 (Price Change)\n- 换手率 (Turnover Rate)\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773108010389}}
{"type":"message","id":"b624d1d3","parentId":"8941b516","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:00:10.392Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f2f6b1c49d364a7db209d0dc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n### 通用规则\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n### 个股专属规则\n**中国石油 (601857.SH)**:\n- 🟢 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警\n- 🔴 跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773108010391}}
{"type":"message","id":"95d2616a","parentId":"b624d1d3","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:00:10.395Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_944f3e4778b646b38ab7f835","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773108010393}}
