{"type":"message","id":"b011f3c2","parentId":"da29269f","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:00:22.450Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f6a9456f1d574d6896ab3945","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"601857|中国石油\n601808|中海油服\n600256|广汇能源\n600583|海油工程\n000852|石化机械\n600547|山东黄金\n601069|西部黄金\n600988|赤峰黄金\n000975|银泰黄金\n002716|金贵银业\n601899|紫金矿业\n9866.HK|蔚来-SW\nAAPL|苹果\n920876|慧为智能\n688111|金山办公\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773108022446}}
